          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">For each ranged attack made by another friendly Astra Militarum unit that targets an enemy unit visible to this unit, reroll a Hit Roll of 1 for that attack.</characteristic>
